g.aria-label: Perform for each run: aggregation of peptides found in multiple files as the average of ratios
Perform for each report file: 1. peptide sequences retrieval from PD sequences 2. re-annotation of PTMs 3. averaging PSM ratios per peptide
Perform for every sample: 1. log2 transformation 2. zero center normalization by median 3. rescale to the common reference channel
Remove PSMs: 1. with identification q-value < 0.01 2. without reporter ions labels ("No Quan Labels") 3. having PTMs of ptmRS localization score < 90 4. that the reference channel is NA
